emotes.msg: Those pyramids that attacked the towns have become stationary around this pit.
We need warriors that have no fear to find a way into those pyramids and find out what is going on.
If you find any of those stones they were collecting before please bring them to me so that we may study them.
Collect 30 of each type of stone you find and I'll reward you for your trouble.
